thread.title_full: Express Medical Supply reviewed by Livette Marshall

author: Livette Marshall
title: Livette Marshall
text: I am very happy with the catheters I purchased. They are perfect size. I also am very appreciative for the self lubed catheters to go. They are small and easily fit in my purse. All the products are of excellent quality and I usually receive my orders within 2 business days.
